# Streamlit Application Assembly

Thin shell in **`app.py`**; sidebar/upload/configure live in split modules. Delegate ingest/build to **`app_services.py`** and rendering to **`pipeline.build_cross_section()`** â†’ **`CrossSectionResult`**.

## Module split

| Module | Role |
|--------|------|
| `app.py` | `set_page_config`, session init, workflow routing, generate + staleness |
| `app_sidebar.py` | Sidebar: layout, style, consulting title block, Advanced water/GW toggles, transect thresholds, import/AI |
| `app_upload.py` | Welcome card, workbook detect/parse |
| `app_build.py` | `collect_section_build_request()`, `generate_cross_section()` |
| `app_styles.py` | Shared CSS (`APP_CSS`) |
| `app_common.py` | Shared helpers (assistant, transect selection, quality refresh, legend) |
| `app_validate.py` | Validate step: Data Health, fix plan, lithology mapping, sheet roles |
| `app_configure.py` | Configure: transect sidebar, correlation health, manual overrides, section Q&A |
| `app_generate.py` | Generate, stale banner, SVG/PNG/PDF downloads |
| `app_menubar.py` | Windows-style File/Edit/View/Help menus, Ctrl accelerators, `docs/help` dialogs |
| `app_state.py` | `DEFAULT_SESSION` + domain key groups / clear helpers |
| `app_services.py` | Streamlit `@st.cache_data` wrappers only (no widgets, no geometry); engine stays Streamlit-free |
| `ui_helpers.py` | Streamlit-free helpers: `active_transect_selection`, `svg_is_valid`, workflow stage |
| `ui_output_presets.py` | Named output presets â†’ sidebar / `SectionBuildRequest` field mapping |
| `section_build_request.py` | Frozen `SectionBuildRequest` + unified `cache_key()` |

## Integration Pattern

```python
parse_result, import_report = cached_ingest_workbook(uploaded_bytes, ...)
request = SectionBuildRequest(...)
subset = subset_parse_result(parse_result, active_hole_ids, lithology_index=...)
result = cached_build_section(subset.model_dump_json(), request.model_dump_json())
# â†’ SVG-first CrossSectionResult; primary Prepare PNG & PDF via cached_build_section_exports(); secondary per-format via cached_build_section_png / cached_build_section_pdf
```

- **Primary cache key:** `SectionBuildRequest.cache_key(hole_ids)` in `st.session_state.render_cache_key`
- **Transect selection cache:** `app_common.active_transect_selection_cached()` memoizes `ui_helpers.active_transect_selection()`
- **Session keys:** `DEFAULT_SESSION` in `app_state.py`; use `clear_section_output_state()` / domain clears
- **SVG display:** `st.markdown` + base64 `<img>` via `svg_display_meta()` â€” never `st.image()` on raw SVG
- **Lazy imports** for `ai_assistant` / `render_theme` inside helpers (avoid Streamlit hot-reload ImportErrors)

## Workflow (four steps)

**Upload â†’ Validate â†’ Configure â†’ Generate**

1. **Upload** â€” file uploader, profile, CRS, elevation, Parse; import report (optional sheets, geology counts, `unit_order`)
2. **Validate** â€” Data Health, fix-path coach, lithology mapping, sheet roles, QA narrative
3. **Configure** â€” transect (incl. NL pick), correlation health + AI link suggestions, section Q&A, consulting report sheet fields
4. **Generate** â€” warnings gate, `cached_build_section()` (**SVG only**), overlap warnings; primary **Prepare PNG & PDF** via `cached_build_section_exports()`; secondary per-format via `cached_build_section_png` / `cached_build_section_pdf`

## Layouts

- `section_sheet`, `consulting_section`, `chart` via `render_layout`
- Lithology fills use BH Log legend colours via `get_lithology_style()` (constants aliased as `USGS_LITHOLOGY_*`); legend in title block
- Optional workbook sheets: **Screens**, **Gradients** (see `docs/workbook-format.md`)

## Boundaries

- Widgets only in `app*.py`; `app_services.py` = cache wrappers only (may import Streamlit for `@st.cache_data`)
- Do not import stratigraphy/projection in UI except QA helpers (`off_transect_warnings`, `suggest_offset_threshold_m`)
- No stratigraphy or projection logic in Streamlit modules
